OL,3,CMajority vote to establish climate
OL,4,Ccomissioner despite cost concern
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,7,FMichelle O'Neill has welcomed the
OL,8,Fpassing of a vote to establish a
OL,9,Fclimate commissioner.
OL,11,FThe DUP opposed the motion at the
OL,12,FAssembly on Tuesday, arguing the costs
OL,13,Fof the role, estimated to be #1
OL,14,Fmillion a year, could not be justified
OL,15,Fin the current financial climate.
OL,17,FHowever, the draft Northern Ireland
OL,18,FClimate Commissioner Regulations 2025
OL,19,Fwere passed by 51 votes to 19.
