OL,4,Ccomissioner despite cost concern
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters in the Great
OL,7,FHall at Parliament Buildings, Ms
OL,8,FO'Neill said it was regrettable the
OL,9,FDUP had voted against the plans.
OL,11,FShe said: "I think that the public can
OL,12,Ftake some comfort that the majority of
OL,13,FMLAs elected here understand that
OL,14,Fclimate is a real emergency,
OL,15,Funderstand that as we speak today the
OL,16,FMournes are on fire, Lough Neagh is in
OL,17,Fcrisis, floods are becoming an ever
OL,18,Fmore occurring phenomenon.
