OL,3,CMajority vote to establish climate
OL,4,Ccomissioner despite cost concern
OL,6,F"The cost of doing nothing will be
OL,7,Ffar, far more than the cost of putting
OL,8,Fa commissioner in place that can
OL,9,Factually hold every department and
OL,10,Fagency to account in terms of their
OL,11,Fresponsibility around getting us to
OL,12,Fnet zero by 2050."
OL,14,FLast week, deputy First Minister Emma
OL,15,FLittle-Pengelly said she did not
OL,16,Fbelieve there was a need for a climate
OL,17,Fcommissioner.
