OL,6,FShe said then the appointment will be
OL,7,Fmade because it is a "legal duty", but
OL,8,Fexpressed concern it would cost at
OL,9,Fleast #1 million per year at a time of
OL,10,Ffinancial challenge.
OL,12,F"I don't think that there is a
OL,13,Fparticular need for a climate
OL,14,Fcommissioner at this time, but it is a
OL,15,Flegal duty that falls to the First
OL,16,FMinister and myself, and that's why we
OL,17,Fare moving forward at this time," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
